Georgios Karagounis - Matches in European Cups

Georgios Karagounis has played 69 matches (8 goals) for Panathinaikos (1999-2003 and 2007-now), 7 matches (no goals) for Internazionale and 16 matches (no goals) for Benfica (Lisboa). He played his first match on September 16, 1999 against Gorica.
